00:13:27,306 --> 00:13:29,308
-What's the matter?
-Hmm?

254
00:13:29,392 --> 00:13:30,768
Riko?

255
00:13:30,852 --> 00:13:33,438
Does that mean he had a good time today?

256
00:13:33,521 --> 00:13:35,732
