257
00:13:35,815 --> 00:13:37,316
Are you happy?

258
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,193
Yeah, I'm happy.

259
00:13:39,986 --> 00:13:41,571
Have fun!

260
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:45,825
-Riko totally panicked.
-Totally.

261
00:13:45,908 --> 00:13:47,952
