since a couple has formed.

262
00:13:48,035 --> 00:13:49,328
-I know!
-I know!

263
00:13:49,412 --> 00:13:50,830
-How nice.
-Agreed.

264
00:13:50,913 --> 00:13:52,874
-They're practically together.
-You think so?

265
00:13:52,957 --> 00:13:55,960
