when Hayato acts more masculine,

268
00:14:03,468 --> 00:14:06,053
-and how Riko reacts.
-I see, I see.

269
00:14:06,137 --> 00:14:10,975
Will Riko reject Hayato
when he shows his masculine side?

270
00:14:11,058 --> 00:14:13,645
Or is she going to be able to accept him?

271
00:14:13,728 --> 00:14:17,565
