if he comes onto her with hungry eyes.

272
00:14:17,649 --> 00:14:21,861
And let's not forget,
Hansan is super cool this episode.

273
00:14:21,944 --> 00:14:22,987
Yes, Hansan!

274
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:27,409
