I'd want to squeeze him!

278
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,377
-He's so cute!
-Right?

279
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,879
I'd cook everything I know for him.

280
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:45,677
And then Riko said, "But it was raining,
and it was crowded..."

281
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,887
And as he listens...

282
00:14:47,970 --> 00:14:50,640
"It was raining, it was crowded... but?"

283
00:14:50,723 --> 00:14:52,349
Yeah, the "but"!

284
00:14:53,685 --> 00:14:55,269
The way he said that was so cute!

285
00:14:55,352 --> 00:14:57,939
I'd strip his pants off right there!

286
00:14:58,773 --> 00:15:00,149
Time out!

