387
00:20:30,021 --> 00:20:31,731
Are you having fun?

388
00:20:31,814 --> 00:20:33,524
Yeah, I am.

389
00:20:33,607 --> 00:20:35,067
Does everyone get along?

390
00:20:35,151 --> 00:20:38,320
