had fights.

391
00:20:38,404 --> 00:20:39,989
But there aren't any right now.

392
00:20:40,072 --> 00:20:41,698
How's your love life?

393
00:20:42,909 --> 00:20:45,327
Well, I went on two dates with a guy.

394
00:20:45,411 --> 00:20:46,996
Oh, yeah?

395
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:52,043
I like him,
but I don't know if I like-like him yet.

396
00:20:52,126 --> 00:20:56,088
Well... he's 11 years older.

397
00:20:56,172 --> 00:20:58,174
Hey, that's cool.

398
00:20:58,257 --> 00:20:59,759
What do you think about that?

399
00:20:59,842 --> 00:21:02,344
-I'm totally okay with it.
-Really?

400
00:21:02,428 --> 00:21:04,513
Take my parents, for example.

401
00:21:04,638 --> 00:21:06,766
My dad's 11 years older
than my mom.

402
00:21:06,849 --> 00:21:09,811
Wow, really?

403
00:21:09,894 --> 00:21:13,647
-I think it's more common now.
-You think so?

404
00:21:14,774 --> 00:21:17,985
That changes things for me.

405
00:21:18,069 --> 00:21:19,361
Is he cute?

406
00:21:19,445 --> 00:21:21,488
I think he is.

407
00:21:21,572 --> 00:21:26,118
So you don't know if you like him yet,
but are you willing to give it a chance?

408
00:21:26,911 --> 00:21:28,120
I think so.

