414
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:53,270
-A pepper?
-Marinated pepper.

415
00:21:53,354 --> 00:21:55,439
A friend of mine runs
a barbecue restaurant.

416
00:21:56,398 --> 00:21:59,193
-He asked me to think of an appetizer.
-Oh, cool.

417
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:03,197
-Aren't you drinking tonight?
