00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:11,205
-once I have my own restaurant.
-Totally.

421
00:22:11,288 --> 00:22:13,582
Your future restaurant, right?
A pasta specialty restaurant?

422
00:22:13,665 --> 00:22:15,292
Yeah, exactly.

423
00:22:15,376 --> 00:22:18,754
