to look like a burger joint.

424
00:22:18,838 --> 00:22:20,882
-That's what you said, right?
-Yup.

425
00:22:20,965 --> 00:22:24,218
And also to have the feel of a resort.

426
00:22:24,301 --> 00:22:29,056
That's cool. It'd be fun to design it
because you don't see anything like it.

427
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:30,641
Exactly.

428
00:22:33,435 --> 00:22:34,811
-Welcome home.
-Thanks.

429
00:22:34,896 --> 00:22:37,982
-What are you doing?
-I'm browning the pepper.

430
00:22:38,065 --> 00:22:39,984
-I'm not playing.
-It looks like it.

431
00:22:40,067 --> 00:22:41,318
Well, I'm not.

432
00:22:41,402 --> 00:22:44,071
-Are you working, Hansan?
-Yes.

433
00:22:44,155 --> 00:22:48,951
I only have about 40 minutes
until I have to send it in.

434
00:22:49,952 --> 00:22:51,453
I'm pretty screwed.

435
00:22:51,537 --> 00:22:54,415
-You are.
-That thing you're working on now?

436
00:22:54,498 --> 00:22:56,292
I'm gonna have to seriously tackle this.

437
00:22:56,375 --> 00:22:59,045
-Good luck.
-I've got 42 minutes.

438
00:22:59,128 --> 00:23:01,923
-Come get me when the peppers are done.
-Okay.

439
00:23:05,676 --> 00:23:07,636
-So...
-Yeah?

440
00:23:09,638 --> 00:23:11,598
-About our date.
