445
00:23:26,905 --> 00:23:27,990
I see.

446
00:23:28,074 --> 00:23:29,951
Out of curiosity, what did you search?

447
00:23:30,034 --> 00:23:31,618
Just...

448
00:23:33,996 --> 00:23:36,958
-I just googled "date."
-That's good.

449
00:23:37,041 --> 00:23:39,293
